casebody.data:
[Merrimack,

December, 1885.] Brown v. Spaulding. ■Case, for crim. con. Facts found by tbe court. Davis Paige and F. H. Gould, for tbe plaintiff. Albin Martin, for the defendant. Doe, C. J.

It does not appear that tbe plaintiff’s original cause of action was extinguished by bis subsequent prospective agreement.

Case discharged.

Carpenter, J., did not sit: the others concurred.
